name: React Native Airbnb
tagline: Airbnb® Clone built with React Native
body:
### Welcome to Airbnb Clone built with React Native.

Tech Stack 
* react
* react-native
* flux/redux
* firebase

### Authors and Contributors
You can @mention a GitHub username to generate a link to their profile. The resulting `<a>` element will link to the contributor’s GitHub Profile.
 
example: Marco Argentieri (@tiero), founder (https://github.com/vulpemcom)

### Support or Contact
Having trouble? [contact support](https://github.com/contact) and we’ll help you sort it out.
